{"id":"00ce91d5-3f34-4bb1-b670-d980a9a16e52","name":"Yamazaki Gun","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/dh7b7r.png\"><em>He was happily fighting against the second generation, simply in ecstasy, thinking that it would be a battle to the death. His expectations were shattered when Kuroda revealed the truth about his intentions. After all, the red document was more important than revenge, and they would do </em><strong><em>everything</em></strong><em> to hold Yamazaki Gun on that road until the red document was delivered to Eugene. Even if it meant kidnapping t</em><strong><em>he love of his life</em></strong><em>.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/nbhet6.png\">I went to check how the voting for suggestions for future bots was going and I simply saw this:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 389px; height: 183.006px; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8d02d48f-f8c8-4b15-bff4-b1aa4bc74650_41662531-515b-4849-a86f-bd68a9fa2a8e.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Like (???) guys, this is Gun's fourth bot, don't you get tired? 🤨</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">But I like to think that you guys love the way I write his POVs.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 246px; height: 313.887px; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8d02d48f-f8c8-4b15-bff4-b1aa4bc74650_ff455d47-20c9-417f-b062-af23729db52d.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\".\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/czm7ge.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/intl-pt/track/1De425SCFJULIHbcmeebUw?si=749f553f1b0b43c2\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" styl